name: Post
description: PopulateChunkEvent.Post is fired just after a chunk is populated with a terrain feature. This event is fired just after terrain feature generation in ChunkProviderEnd.populate(int, int) , ChunkProviderOverworld.populate(int, int) , and ChunkProviderHell.populate(int, int) . This event is not Cancelable . This event does not have a result. HasResult This event is fired on the MinecraftForge.EVENT_BUS .
